      "text": [
        " : سَأَلْتُ أَبَا عَبْدِ اَللَّهِ عَلَيْهِ اَلسَّلاَمُ أَ يَجُوزُ لِلْمُسْلِمِ أَنْ يُعْتِقَ مَمْلُوكاً مُشْرِكاً قَالَ \"لاَ\"."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.3523 - It is narrated from Saif bin Amira, who said:\n\"I asked Abu Abdullah (as), 'Is it permissible for a Muslim to free a slave who is a polytheist?'\"\nImam (as) said: \"No.\""
